title: Open Weekends For Tour-Newly Renovated-Luxury Amenities-Great Location
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-The Cinema Offers Cozy Seating for Private Viewing Parties', '-Heated, Underground Garage Stalls Available with Convenient Car Washing Station', '-High Intensity UVC Lamp Coupled with Bionic iWave Air Purifying Systems', '-Payments', 'Accepted: Credit Card, Cash via MoneyGram, Apple Pay and FREE E-Check', '-Promenade Bike Trail and Bicycle Storage', '-24-Hour Fitness Center Furnished with Life Fitness Equipment', '-Package Concierge Offering 24-Hour Access to Packages', '-The Event Features a Demonstration Kitchen with Enough Room to Entertain a Few Close Friends or a Crowd', '-Over 20,000 Sq Ft of Amenities!', '-Spacious, walk-in closets in select apartment homes', '-The Patio Offerings a Peaceful Outdoor Lounging Space, Accented with Four Gas Grills and a Gas Fire Pit', '-Walk in showers in select two and three bedroom apartments', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
